<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Behavioral_economics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Anomalies (economic behavior)">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Anomalies (economic behavior)</span></h3>
